data.description: Welcome to your ideal home in Waters Edge, Port Orange, Florida! This impeccably maintained residence offers both convenience and charm, situated near the Pavilion with its array of amenities and close proximity to I-4 for easy commuting to Orlando or Saint Augustine. Known for its well-kept surroundings, Waters Edge is perfect for families or retirees seeking a serene community atmosphere.Inside, you'll find a spacious and inviting interior with beautiful flooring and an open-concept layout, ideal for modern living. The split floor plan ensures privacy and functionality, catering to diverse lifestyles. Step onto the expansive back porch to enjoy tranquil views of the pond, where ducks gracefully swim, adding to the peaceful ambiance. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this home yours and experience the epitome of Florida living. Schedule your showing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in Waters Edge.
